<Content>Hospitality Inn If you're looking for hospitality at your next lodging, you will find it here. The proprietors are warm, friendly and kind. They graciously try to help me out with whatever needs I have when I arrive. It's a cozy and comfortable little getaway place. Their office serves as the lobby and has a warm fireplace inside with a beautiful waterfall courtyard outside; they serve complimentary cookies and tea in the evenings, and in the morning they offer pastries, fruit and coffee/tea; a perfect place to sit and relax after I take a walk. And all of this comes with a big smile... always! The area around the Inn is great for taking walks and, if you want to, you can even walk to a restaurant of your choice for dinner or whatever. I'm glad I discovered The Brentwood Inn. It's where I always stay when I am in Los Angeles near UCLA. 
